          <text x="600" y="348" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">rules are explicit</text>
          <text x="600" y="365" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">owner is named</text>
          <text x="600" y="382" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">ledger is defensible</text>
          <text x="600" y="399" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">AI is bounded and replaceable</text>
